# Minimal test case for internal stream definition.
# This tests if the behavior of an internal stream (x1) can be defined after the REPL enters history mode.

# --- Streams ---
tau i1 = console
tau o1 = console
tau x1 = console # Internal stream

# --- Logic ---
# This first rule for a primary output stream (o1) will succeed and enter history mode.
o1[t] = i1[t]

# This second rule for an internal stream (x1) is expected to fail.
x1[t] = i1[t]
